  "local_port": 44668,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can I find a free online course to learn WordPress themes management?",
  "response": "There are several platforms that offer free online courses to learn WordPress theme management. Here are some reputable options you can consider:\n\n1. **WordPress.org**:\n   - WordPress offers free tutorials and guides on its official site. You can find a section dedicated to themes, where you can learn about installing, customizing, and managing themes.\n   - **Link**: [WordPress Theme Handbook](https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/)\n\n2. **Coursera**:\n   - Coursera provides free courses from universities and institutions. You can look for courses that cover WordPress theme management, often as part of a broader web development or content management curriculum.\n   - **Example Course**: \"Introduction to Web Development\" might have segments on WordPress theme management.\n   - **Link**: [Coursera](https://www.coursera.org/)\n\n3. **edX**:\n   - Similar to Coursera, edX offers courses from top universities. You can search for courses related to WordPress and focus on the segments about theme management.\n   - **Example Course**: \"Web Design: Wireframes to Prototypes\" might cover WordPress theme customization.\n   - **Link**: [edX](https://www.edx.org/)\n\n4. **Udemy**:\n   - While Udemy primarily offers paid courses, you can often find free ones during promotions. Look for courses specifically about WordPress theme management.\n   - **Example Course**: \"WordPress Theme Development with Bootstrap\" might have free sections during promotions.\n   - **Link**: [Udemy](https://www.udemy.com/)\n\n5. **freeCodeCamp**:\n   - freeCodeCamp offers free coding courses and has a section on WordPress where you can learn how to manage and develop themes.\n   - **Link**: [freeCodeCamp WordPress Tutorials](https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/tag/wordpress/)\n\n6. **YouTube**:\n   - Many content creators provide free tutorials on YouTube. Channels like \"WPTuts\" and \"WP Beginner\" have extensive tutorials on WordPress theme management.\n   - **Example Channel**: [WP Beginner](https://www.youtube.com/user/wpbeginner)\n\n7. **Skillshare**:\n   - Skillshare sometimes offers free trials, and you can find courses on WordPress theme management. They cover a variety of topics related to web design and WordPress.\n   - **Example Course**: \"WordPress Theme Customization for Beginners\"\n   - **Link**: [Skillshare](https://www.skillshare.com/)\n\nBefore enrolling, make sure to check the course syllabus to ensure it covers the aspects of WordPress theme management you are interested in, such as installation, customization, and troubleshooting.",
